channel.title: Where can I find a Clean Source?
channel.description:
Hello,
I am looking to build my server completely from scratch. I have had a few servers in the past for learning measures, and was looking instead of encountering all the bugs from getting a source, that I would instead build my own from the ground up. I remember back years ago when WhiteKastle (sp?) had a clean source for 317 (Sp?) and I am pretty good with Java. I would like a newer rev, but I can always just get a new one and get the keys to update it. A newer one would however save me time on doing that.
Thanks, Delaura
